FAQ常问问题

What is Ark Protocol?什么是方舟协议？

Ark is a multichain identity linking protocol built to power decent.land, ANS, and any other applications that rely on users attesting to their identity on other chains. Example use cases include token gating and social data aggregation. With Ark, users can use their Arweave wallet as a master identity to prove activity on multiple other chains.Ark 是一种多链身份链接协议，旨在为 decent.land、ANS 和任何其他依赖用户在其他链上证明其身份的应用程序提供支持。示例用例包括令牌门控和社交数据聚合。通过方舟，用户可以使用他们的 Arweave 钱包作为主身份来证明在多个其他链上的活动。

Who built Ark?谁建造了方舟？

Ark was built by the decent.land team and is one of the project's core social protocols along with ANS and the Public Square.Ark 由 decent.land 团队打造，与 ANS 和 Public Square 一起是该项目的核心社交协议之一。

Why did decent.land build Ark?为什么 decent.land 建造方舟？

decent.land is a collection of social and identity primitives built on Arweave to support the creation of token-gated social networks and groups. The core contracts live on Arweave but interact with other chains to build a chain-agnostic way to save your identity and control access to DAO discussions and governance.Ark is our way to verifiably associate any number of Ethereum/EVM chain addresses with an Arweave wallet or ANS profile, and makes it so our other protocols can read token holdings and activity from Ethereum, Avalanche, BNB Chain, Aurora, Polygon, and more. decent.land 是建立在 Arweave 上的社会和身份原语的集合，以支持创建代币门控的社交网络和团体。核心合约存在于 Arweave 上，但与其他链交互以构建一种与链无关的方式来保存您的身份并控制对 DAO 讨论和治理的访问。 Ark 是我们将任意数量的以太坊/EVM 链地址与 Arweave 钱包或 ANS 配置文件可验证地关联起来的方法，并使我们的其他协议可以从以太坊、Avalanche、BNB Chain、Aurora、Polygon 等读取代币持有量和活动.

What do I need to start?我需要什么开始？

You need the ArConnect extension to get an Arweave wallet and sign Arweave transactions. It should have enough AR for the interaction, e.g. 0.01 AR.You need either Metamask, Coinbase Wallet or a Wallet Connect compatible Ethereum wallet extension and a wallet on Ethereum mainnet, with enough ETH for gas, e.g. 0.0005 ETH.Connect both wallets on the UI, confirm the transactions, and the data will populate on Arweave. 您需要 ArConnect 扩展来获取 Arweave 钱包并签署 Arweave 交易。它应该有足够的 AR 来进行交互，例如0.01 应收账款。 您需要 Metamask、Coinbase 钱包或兼容 Wallet Connect 的以太坊钱包扩展和以太坊主网上的钱包，并有足够的 ETH 用于 gas，例如0.0005 以太币。 在 UI 上连接两个钱包，确认交易，数据将填充到 Arweave 上。

What can I do once my identities are linked with Ark?身份绑定方舟后怎么办？

We are building token-gating protocols for both Telegram and the upcoming decent.land web app. We are also working on aggregation of multichain data for the ANS identity layer, to show activity from any chain on your own ar.page profile.Early Ark adopters may be eligible for future beta testing opportunities as we expand the set of protocols and use cases我们正在为 Telegram 和即将推出的 decent.land 网络应用构建令牌门控协议。我们还致力于为 ANS 身份层聚合多链数据，以在您自己的 ar.page 配置文件中显示来自任何链的活动。 随着我们扩展协议和用例集，早期方舟采用者可能有资格获得未来的 Beta 测试机会

How can I build on Ark Protocol?我如何在方舟协议上构建？

If your dApp deals with verifying a user’s identity across chains, or is an Arweave dApp built to work with other L1s, Ark Protocol could be a useful primitive to integrate.Check it on GitHub here.如果您的 dApp 处理跨链验证用户身份，或者是为与其他 L1 一起工作而构建的 Arweave dApp，Ark Protocol 可能是一个有用的集成原语。在 GitHub 上查看它。

Why is it called Ark?为什么叫方舟呢？

In the decent.land lore, settlers arrived on the planet on a fleet of arks - spaceships ranging in size from personal craft to floating cities. Like its spacefaring namesake, the Ark Protocol makes connections between distant environments.在 decent.land 传说中，定居者乘坐方舟舰队抵达地球 - 大小从个人飞船到漂浮城市的宇宙飞船。就像它的太空同名一样，方舟协议在遥远的环境之间建立联系。
